calculateItinerary(String[]) - Method in class ui.clui.CommandLineController
This method applies command line instructions of the form:
calculateItinerary <networkName> <userID> <startX> <startY> <destinationX> <destinationY> <pathStrategy>
The pathStrategy can be minimal-walking, fastest-path, prefer-plus, avoid-plus, or uniformity.
calculateItinerary(Point, Point, PathStrategy) - Method in class user.User

This method calculates an itinerary given a starting position, an arrival position and a PathStrategy, and considering the BikeType wanted.
